jQuery Bubble Plugin
originally created by Â± ryan, 2010

Provides the ability to add various types of 'bubbles' to the interface, like tooltips, context menus, modals, dialogs, etc.

jquery.bubble.js:
The plugin itself. Built for jQuery 1.3.x, should be forward-compatible with the 1.4.x line, although could be optimized further for that version.

jquery.js:
jQuery 1.3.x. Included for reference and for the benefit of the examples utilizing the plugin.

examples:
Various example(s) of the bubble in action.
